{"tid":930680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★一群大媽在車禍現場大跳大媽舞，阻礙救援！","createTime":"2018-12-06T13:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T13:40:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5ab1234a7fd0b1445238d3a49e65c3b6f0011797","tid":930680,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:00:45.000Z","msg":"12月1日，江西贛州高速路段發生了一起車禍。因處理事故，造成高速路暫時擁堵，許多車輛都在停車等待。而距離車禍現場只有500米的地方，一群大媽們竟然在應急車道上歡快的跳起了廣場舞。引來很多的人下車拍照圍觀，好不歡快。簡直和前方悲慘的車禍形成了鮮明的對比，讓人看了實在寒心，難受。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GeiKLe3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGeiKLe3.gif&h=d266be85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://3g.163.com/dy/article/E29EB3PO0529PUHD.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F3g.163.com%2Fdy%2Farticle%2FE29EB3PO0529PUHD.html&d=BK1g1eN8jI%2B4p8cgbZaFdNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=21fa8a5d\" target=\"_blank\">http://3g.163.com/dy/article/E29EB3PO0529PUHD.html</a><br />\n一群大媽們穿著紅的、黃的各色的衣服、運動鞋。其中有兩名大媽戴著棒球帽，似乎是領舞，跳得最是歡脫，從音樂起就一直沒有停。隊中似乎還有男子參與，一行有七八個人。他們在應急車道上排排站，有隊有形，自顧自得跳開了。面對眾人的圍觀拍照，他們似乎還很驕傲得意，覺得是一件特別自豪有面子的事情。<br />\n<br />\n交警發現這一不文明的違法行為，立即上前勸離。應急車道在高速上是救命用的，不是用來隨意&ldquo;撒歡&rdquo;的。而且在高度路上遇到擁堵，行人是不能隨意下車走動的。佔用應急車道跳廣場是堅決不允許的，不僅影響救援車輛的正常通行，自身安全也沒有保障。"},{"pid":"2416154c2087ad131fe1f627db7e93fab706a8d4","tid":930680,"uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hy2GNvd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHy2GNvd.jpg&h=4a35ac89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7d96be4dda6394525cafb1214f0ef28fbc56297","tid":930680,"uid":29080,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"起了鼓舞作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ebb28786f28a1f1ed62e6325860bf74c737c15","tid":930680,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ae85f34a3d7880f49edb784c2ae7f7556b6a3f","tid":930680,"uid":179467,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:11:56.000Z","msg":"紅衛兵的死淨種幾時先全部夠鐘去地府報到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315a8d98ce7d8d0784d7349287aae403cc0d5a62","tid":930680,"uid":13638,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:12:38.000Z","msg":"呢個時候應該有架車車飛哂佢地.gif"},{"pid":"c631b7d2b7cef3af8226b0412f60d08e3656aaad","tid":930680,"uid":14103,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:28:16.000Z","msg":"係舞孃？ 幫人加buff呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fff6440bd87347f48dc606b82ab41b80becd35","tid":930680,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"c631b7d2b7cef3af8226b0412f60d08e3656aaad","tid":930680,"uid":14103,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:28:16.000Z","msg":"係舞孃？ 幫人加buff呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:30:17.000Z","msg":"你講緊乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7dbe70e52064139eaab96009847540c5829ae71","tid":930680,"uid":61882,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T14:41:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>12月1日，江西贛州高速路段發生了<span style=\"color: red;\">一起車禍</span>。</blockquote><br />\n一起車禍，一起跳舞<br />\n這就是中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4610c8a26102bad899e193f4493d8f176895aaa","tid":930680,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19fff6440bd87347f48dc606b82ab41b80becd35","tid":930680,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"c631b7d2b7cef3af8226b0412f60d08e3656aaad","tid":930680